      "source": [
        "***Categorising Corpus***\n",
        "\n",
        "The dataset was divided into three sub-corpora according to 1 of the 3 distinct subjects of respective poems.\n",
        "\n",
        "Because these poems revolve around clearly different subjects the entire dataset as a single corpus would risk skewed results, especially considering different amounts of poems for each subject.\n",
        "\n",
        "To address this, tokenised texts were filtered according to their corpus label and stored separately. This allowed topic modelling to be performed within each subject's purview rather than across fundamentally different subject domains.\n"
      ],
