      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        ">*Extracting Enjambment for the Poems Closesly Read*\n",
        ">\n",
        ">*While a proportion is a useful metric, it would be much more fruitful to see how accurate the enjambment search is for the poems by taking a few example cases. The closely read poems (A28, A37, C01, C04, L04, L11) are now run through a function to find the enjambed lines such that they may be cross-verified.*"
